library(vegan)
## Loading required package: permute
## Loading required package: lattice
## This is vegan 2.3-5
library(MASS)
data(BCI)
mod <- decorana(BCI)
plot(mod)

names(BCI)[1:5]
## [1] "Abarema.macradenia"    "Acacia.melanoceras"    "Acalypha.diversifolia"
## [4] "Acalypha.macrostachya" "Adelia.triloba"
shnam <- make.cepnames(names(BCI))
shnam[1:5]
## [1] "Abarmacr" "Acacmela" "Acaldive" "Acalmacr" "Adeltril"
pl <- plot(mod, dis="sp")
identify(pl, "sp", labels=shnam)

## integer(0)
stems <- colSums(BCI)
plot(mod, dis="sp", type="n")
sel<- orditorp(mod, dis="sp", lab=shnam, priority=stems, pcol = "grey")
